## Configuration Reference

### Lambda Environment Variables

| Variable | Production | Testing | Description |
|----------|-----------|---------|-------------|
| `CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD` | 0.80 | 0.70 | Min confidence to deploy |
| `ENABLE_AUTO_DEPLOY` | true | false | Auto-deploy adjustments |
| `DRY_RUN` | false | true | Log only, don't deploy |
| `MAX_WORKERS` | 10 | 5 | Parallel analysis workers |

**Change environment variables**:
```bash
aws lambda update-function-configuration \
  --function-name betbudai-learning-orchestrator \
  --environment "Variables={
    CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD=0.80,
    ENABLE_AUTO_DEPLOY=true,
    DRY_RUN=false,
    MAX_WORKERS=10
  }" \
  --region eu-west-1
```

### Pattern Detection Thresholds

| Threshold | Default | Description |
|-----------|---------|-------------|
| **Pattern Frequency** | 20% | Min % of races to trigger pattern |
| **Confidence Base** | Varies | Base confidence per pattern type |
| **Confidence Boost** | +10% | Per 10% frequency increase |
| **Max Change** | ±50% | Max weight change per adjustment |

### DynamoDB Tables

| Table | Purpose | Billing | TTL |
|-------|---------|---------|-----|
| `SureBetBets` | Main data source | PAY_PER_REQUEST | None |
| `BetBudAI_LearningInsights` | Learning sessions | PAY_PER_REQUEST | 90 days |
| `BetBudAI_WeightChangelog` | Weight history | PAY_PER_REQUEST | None |

